# slimesplash
[Upload<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8"><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
<title>FPS Slime — sombras, espada, história</title>
<style>
  html,body{margin:0;background:#000;color:#eee;font-family:system-ui,Arial;overflow:hidden}
  canvas{display:block;margin:auto;image-rendering:pixelated;border:2px solid #222;border-radius:12px}
  .hud{position:fixed;left:10px;top:10px;display:flex;gap:12px;align-items:center;pointer-events:none}
  .pill{padding:4px 8px;border:1px solid #333;border-radius:999px;background:#111}
  .btn{position:fixed;right:10px;top:10px;padding:8px 12px;border-radius:8px;background:#1e1e1e;border:1px solid #333;color:#ddd;cursor:pointer}
#touchControls{position:fixed;inset:0;pointer-events:none;display:none}
#touchControls .pad{position:absolute;bottom:22px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:10px;pointer-events:auto}
#touchControls .left{left:22px}
#touchControls .right{right:22px;align-items:flex-end}
.tbtn{min-width:64px;min-height:64px;border-radius:14px;border:1px solid #333;background:rgba(30,30,30,.6);color:#fff;font-size:18px}
.tbtn.big{min-width:120px;min-height:120px;font-size:20px}
.row{display:flex;gap:10px;justify-content:center}
#crosshair{position:fixed;left:50%;top:50%;width:10px;height:10px;margin-left:-5px;margin-top:-5px;border-radius:50%;border:2px solid rgba(255,255,255,.7);box-shadow:0 0 4px rgba(255,255,255,.4);pointer-events:none}
html,body{touch-action:none;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;overscroll-behavior:none}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<canvas id="game" width="900" height="520"></canvas>
<div id="touchControls">
  <div class="pad left">
    <button class="tbtn" data-key="KeyW">▲</button>
    <div class="row">
      <button class="tbtn" data-key="KeyA">◄</button>
      <button class="tbtn" data-key="KeyS">▼</button>
      <button class="tbtn" data-key="KeyD">►</button>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="pad right">
    <button class="tbtn big" id="btnAttack">ATACAR</button>
    <div class="row">
      <button class="tbtn" id="btnDoor">PORTA</button>
      <button class="tbtn" id="btnSwap">ARMA</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div id="crosshair"></div>
<div class="hud">
  <span class="pill" id="hp"></span>
  <span class="pill" id="score"></span>
  <span class="pill" id="stage"></span>
  <span class="pill" id="weapon"></span>
</div>
<button id="start" class="btn">Clique para jogar</button>

<script>
const canvas=document.getElementById('game'), ctx=canvas.getContext('2d');
let W=canvas.width, H=canvas.height;
const hpEl=document.getElementById('hp'), scoreEl=document.getElementById('score');
const stageEl=document.getElementById('stage'), weaponEl=document.getElementById('weapon');
const startBtn=document.getElementById('start');
function resizeCanvas(){
  const dpr = window.devicePixelRatio || 1;
  const w = window.innerWidth, h = window.innerHeight;
  canvas.style.width = w+'px'; canvas.style.height = h+'px';
  canvas.width = Math.floor(w*dpr); canvas.height = Math.floor(h*dpr);
  W = canvas.width; H = canvas.height;
}
window.addEventListener('resize', resizeCanvas, {passive:true});
resizeCanvas();

// ====== Constants ======
const TILE_EMPTY=0, TILE_WALL=1, TILE_DOOR=2;

// ====== Player & Camera ======
let posX=2.5,posY=2.5, dirX=1,dirY=0, planeX=0,planeY=0.66;
let health=123, score=0, lastTime=0, recoil=0, t=0;
let weapon='gun', hasSword=false;
const damageGun=20, damageSword=45;
let bobT=0, bobAmt=0; // head bob
let zBuffer=new Float32Array(W);

// ====== Stages ======
let STAGE=1, MAX_STAGE=25;
let worldMap=[], MAP_W=18, MAP_H=12;
let doorOpen=false, doorPos={x:0,y:0};

// ====== Enemies ======
const enemies=[]; // {x,y,hp,alive,atkCd,speed,hitFlash}
const enemyImg=new Image(); enemyImg.src="data:image/gif;base64,";
let enemyReady=false; enemyImg.onload=()=>enemyReady=true;

// ====== Textures ======
const wallImg=new Image(); wallImg.src="data:image/jpeg;base64,";
const floorImg=new Image(); floorImg.src="data:image/jpeg;base64,";
const ceilImg=new Image();  ceilImg.src="data:image/jpeg;base64,";
const doorImg=new Image();  doorImg.src="data:image/jpeg;base64,";
let wallReady=false,floorReady=false,ceilReady=false,doorReady=false;
wallImg.onload=()=>wallReady=true; doorImg.onload=()=>doorReady=true;

// Predecode floor/ceil
let floorTexData=null, ftw=0, fth=0;
floorImg.onload=()=>{ const c=document.createElement('canvas'); c.width=floorImg.width; c.height=floorImg.height;
  const cx=c.getContext('2d'); cx.drawImage(floorImg,0,0); const id=cx.getImageData(0,0,c.width,c.height);
  floorTexData=id.data; ftw=c.width; fth=c.height; floorReady=true; };
let ceilTexData=null, ctw=0, cth=0;
ceilImg.onload=()=>{ const c=document.createElement('canvas'); c.width=ceilImg.width; c.height=ceilImg.height;
  const cx=c.getContext('2d'); cx.drawImage(ceilImg,0,0); const id=cx.getImageData(0,0,c.width,c.height);
  ceilTexData=id.data; ctw=c.width; cth=c.height; ceilReady=true; };

// Weapons
const gunImg=new Image();   gunImg.src="data:image/png;base64,";
const swordImg=new Image(); swordImg.src="data:image/png;base64,";
let gunReady=false, swordReady=false; gunImg.onload=()=>gunReady=true; swordImg.onload=()=>swordReady=true;

// Audio
let AC=null, master=null;
function ensureAudio(){ if(!AC){ AC=new (window.AudioContext||window.webkitAudioContext)(); master=AC.createGain(); master.gain.value=0.35; master.connect(AC.destination);}
  AC.resume();
}
function playGunshot(){
  if(!AC) ensureAudio(); const now=AC.currentTime;
  const len=AC.sampleRate*0.16; const buf=AC.createBuffer(1,len,AC.sampleRate); const data=buf.getChannelData(0);
  for(let i=0;i<len;i++){ const tt=i/len; data[i]=(Math.random()*2-1)*(1-tt)*(1-tt);}
  const noise=AC.createBufferSource(); noise.buffer=buf;
  const hp=AC.createBiquadFilter(); hp.type='highpass'; hp.frequency.value=700;
  const g=AC.createGain(); g.gain.setValueAtTime(0.001,now); g.gain.exponentialRampToValueAtTime(0.9,now+0.01); g.gain.exponentialRampToValueAtTime(0.001,now+0.16);
  noise.connect(hp); hp.connect(g); g.connect(master); noise.start(now); noise.stop(now+0.17);
}
function playSlash(){
  if(!AC) ensureAudio(); const now=AC.currentTime;
  const osc=AC.createOscillator(); osc.type='sawtooth'; osc.frequency.setValueAtTime(520,now);
  const g=AC.createGain(); g.gain.setValueAtTime(0.001,now); g.gain.exponentialRampToValueAtTime(0.7,now+0.02); g.gain.exponentialRampToValueAtTime(0.001,now+0.12);
  const hp=AC.createBiquadFilter(); hp.type='highpass'; hp.frequency.value=450; osc.connect(hp); hp.connect(g); g.connect(master); osc.start(now); osc.stop(now+0.12);
}

// Utils & Input
const keys={}; let pointerLocked=false;
function clamp(v,a,b){return Math.max(a,Math.min(b,v));}
function isWallAt(x,y){ const xi=x|0, yi=y|0; if(xi<0||yi<0||xi>=MAP_W||yi>=MAP_H) return true;
  const t=worldMap[yi][xi]; if(t===1) return true; if(t===2 && !doorOpen) return true; return false; }
function dist(a,b,c,d){return Math.hypot(a-c,b-d);}

document.addEventListener('keydown',e=>{keys[e.code]=true;
  if(e.code==='Digit1') weapon='gun';
  if(e.code==='Digit2' && hasSword) weapon='sword';
  if(e.code==='KeyE') tryEnterDoor();
  if(e.code==='Space') triggerAttack();
  if(intro) skipIntro();
});
document.addEventListener('keyup',e=> keys[e.code]=false);
startBtn.addEventListener('click',()=>{canvas.requestPointerLock?.(); ensureAudio(); if(intro) skipIntro();});
document.addEventListener('pointerlockchange',()=>{pointerLocked=(document.pointerLockElement===canvas);
startBtn.textContent = (pointerLocked || isTouch()) ? 'Jogando' : 'Clique para jogar';});
canvas.addEventListener('mousemove',e=>{ if(!pointerLocked) return; rotate(-e.movementX*0.0025); });
canvas.addEventListener('mousedown',()=>{ ensureAudio(); triggerAttack(); if(intro) skipIntro(); });

function rotate(a){const c=Math.cos(a), s=Math.sin(a);
  const odx=dirX; dirX=dirX*c - dirY*s; dirY=odx*s + dirY*c;
  const opx=planeX; planeX=planeX*c - planeY*s; planeY=opx*s + planeY*c;
}

function castRay(px,py,dx,dy,maxDist=1e9){ let mapX=px|0, mapY=py|0;
  const ddx=Math.abs(1/(dx||1e-9)), ddy=Math.abs(1/(dy||1e-9));
  let stepX=(dx<0)?-1:1, stepY=(dy<0)?-1:1;
  let sideX=(dx<0? (px-mapX)*ddx : (mapX+1.0-px)*ddx);
  let sideY=(dy<0? (py-mapY)*ddy : (mapY+1.0-py)*ddy);
  let side=0, dist=0, tile=0;
  while(true){ if(sideX<sideY){ sideX+=ddx; mapX+=stepX; side=0; } else { sideY+=ddy; mapY+=stepY; side=1; }
    if(mapX<0||mapY<0||mapX>=MAP_W||mapY>=MAP_H) break;
    tile=worldMap[mapY][mapX];
    if(tile===1 || (tile===2 && !doorOpen)){ dist=(side===0? sideX-ddx : sideY-ddy); break; }
    if(dist>maxDist) return {hit:false, dist:maxDist, side, tile};
  }
  return {hit:true, dist, side, tile};
}

// FX & attack
const particles=[]; let muzzleTimer=0, slashTimer=0;
function spawnMuzzle(x,y){ muzzleTimer=0.06; for(let i=0;i<14;i++){ const a=(Math.random()*0.6-0.3)-Math.PI/2, s=80+Math.random()*140;
  particles.push({x,y,vx:Math.cos(a)*s,vy:Math.sin(a)*s,life:0,max:0.12,color:'rgba(255,200,120,1)',add:true,size:2}); } }
function spawnImpact(x,y,type){ const n=12; for(let i=0;i<n;i++){ const ang=Math.random()*Math.PI*2, sp=60+Math.random()*120;
  const col= type==='slime' ? (Math.random()<0.5?'rgba(20,255,40,1)':'rgba(140,255,160,1)') : (Math.random()<0.5?'rgba(255,230,180,1)':'rgba(180,180,180,1)');
  particles.push({x,y,vx:Math.cos(ang)*sp,vy:Math.sin(ang)*sp,life:0,max:0.35,color:col,add:type!=='slime',size:2}); } }
function triggerAttack(){ if(weapon==='gun') shootGun(); else slashSword(); }
function shootGun(){ recoil=16; playGunshot();
  const scale=10, iw=gunImg.width*scale, ih=gunImg.height*scale;
  const wx=Math.floor(W-iw-24), wy=Math.floor(H-ih-8-recoil);
  const mx=wx+iw*0.28, my=wy+ih*0.22; spawnMuzzle(mx,my);
  let hitTarget=null, hitD=1e9, sxScreen=W/2;
  const r=castRay(posX,posY,dirX,dirY); hitD=r.dist;
  for(const s of enemies){ if(!s.alive) continue; const vx=s.x-posX, vy=s.y-posY; const d=Math.hypot(vx,vy)||1;
    const ro=castRay(posX,posY,vx/d,vy/d,d); const occluded=ro.hit && ro.dist<d-0.02; if(occluded) continue;
    const invDet=1/(planeX*dirY - dirX*planeY); const tx=invDet*(dirY*vx - dirX*vy); const ty=invDet*(-planeY*vx + planeX*vy);
    if(ty<=0) continue; const sx=(W/2)*(1+tx/ty); const size=Math.abs(H/ty)|0; const left=sx-size*0.45, right=sx+size*0.45;
    if(W/2>=left && W/2<=right && d<hitD){ hitTarget=s; hitD=d; sxScreen=sx; }
  }
  if(hitTarget){ hitTarget.hp-=damageGun; hitTarget.hitFlash=0.12; spawnImpact(sxScreen,H/2,'slime'); if(hitTarget.hp<=0){hitTarget.alive=false; score+=50;} }
  else { const ix=posX+dirX*hitD, iy=posY+dirY*hitD; const dx=ix-posX, dy=iy-posY;
    const invDet=1/(planeX*dirY - dirX*planeY); const tx=invDet*(dirY*dx - dirX*dy); const ty=invDet*(-planeY*dx + planeX*dy);
    if(ty>0){ const sx=(W/2)*(1+tx/ty); spawnImpact(sx,H/2,'wall'); }
  }
}
function slashSword(){ recoil=8; slashTimer=0.14; playSlash();
  let hit=false; for(const s of enemies){ if(!s.alive) continue; const vx=s.x-posX, vy=s.y-posY; const d=Math.hypot(vx,vy)||1;
    if(d>1.6) continue; const dot=(vx*dirX+vy*dirY)/d; if(dot<0.4) continue;
    const ro=castRay(posX,posY,vx/d,vy/d,d); if(ro.hit && ro.dist<d-0.02) continue;
    s.hp-=damageSword; s.hitFlash=0.12; hit=true; if(s.hp<=0){ s.alive=false; score+=50; }
  } if(hit) spawnImpact(W/2,H/2,'slime');
}

// Movement & AI
function tryMove(nx,ny){ const r=0.2;
  if(!isWallAt(nx,posY) && !isWallAt(nx + (nx>posX? r:-r), posY)) posX=nx;
  if(!isWallAt(posX,ny) && !isWallAt(posX, ny + (ny>posY? r:-r))) posY=ny; }
function updateEnemies(dt){ let aliveCount=0;
  for(const s of enemies){ if(!s.alive) continue; aliveCount++;
    const d=dist(posX,posY,s.x,s.y);
    if(d<9){ const vx=(posX-s.x)/d, vy=(posY-s.y)/d; const sp=s.speed*dt;
      const nx=s.x+vx*sp, ny=s.y+vy*sp; if(!isWallAt(nx,s.y)) s.x=nx; if(!isWallAt(s.x,ny)) s.y=ny;
    }
    if(d<1.1 && s.atkCd<=0){ health-=10; s.atkCd=0.8; }
    if(s.atkCd>0) s.atkCd-=dt; if(s.hitFlash>0) s.hitFlash-=dt;
  } if(aliveCount===0 && !doorOpen) doorOpen=true; }

function update(dt){
  const moving = (keys['KeyW']||keys['KeyA']||keys['KeyS']||keys['KeyD']);
  if(moving) bobT += dt*10; else bobT *= (1-4*dt);
  bobAmt = Math.sin(bobT)*6; // pixels
  const sp=3*dt; const mf=(keys['KeyW']?1:0)-(keys['KeyS']?1:0); const ms=(keys['KeyD']?1:0)-(keys['KeyA']?1:0);
  if(mf) tryMove(posX+dirX*sp*mf, posY+dirY*sp*mf); if(ms) tryMove(posX+(-dirY)*sp*ms, posY+(dirX)*sp*ms);
  if(keys['KeyQ']) rotate(+2.5*dt); if(recoil>0) recoil-=50*dt; if(recoil<0) recoil=0; if(muzzleTimer>0) muzzleTimer-=dt; if(slashTimer>0) slashTimer-=dt;
  // particles
  for(let i=particles.length-1;i>=0;i--){ const p=particles[i]; p.life+=dt; if(p.life>p.max){particles.splice(i,1); continue;} const drag=1.0-2.5*dt; p.vx*=drag; p.vy=(p.vy+200*dt)*drag; p.x+=p.vx*dt; p.y+=p.vy*dt; }
  updateEnemies(dt);
}

// Half buffers for floor/ceil
let ceilBufCanvas=null,ceilBufCtx=null,floorBufCanvas=null,floorBufCtx=null;
function ensureHalfBuffer(which, scale=2){ const outW=Math.max(1,(W/scale)|0), outH=Math.max(1,((H/2)/scale)|0);
  if(which==='ceil'){ if(!ceilBufCanvas||ceilBufCanvas.width!==outW||ceilBufCanvas.height!==outH){ ceilBufCanvas=document.createElement('canvas'); ceilBufCanvas.width=outW; ceilBufCanvas.height=outH; ceilBufCtx=ceilBufCanvas.getContext('2d'); }
    return {ctx:ceilBufCtx,canvas:ceilBufCanvas,outW,outH}; }
  else { if(!floorBufCanvas||floorBufCanvas.width!==outW||floorBufCanvas.height!==outH){ floorBufCanvas=document.createElement('canvas'); floorBufCanvas.width=outW; floorBufCanvas.height=outH; floorBufCtx=floorBufCanvas.getContext('2d'); }
    return {ctx:floorBufCtx,canvas:floorBufCanvas,outW,outH}; }
}

// Render
function render(){
  // Teto com bob
  if(ceilReady && ceilTexData){
    const {ctx:cb,canvas:c,outW,outH}=ensureHalfBuffer('ceil',2);
    const img=cb.createImageData(outW,outH), out=img.data;
    const r0x=dirX-planeX, r0y=dirY-planeY, r1x=dirX+planeX, r1y=dirY+planeY;
    for(let j=0;j<outH;j++){ const y=(H/2/outH)*j + 0.5*(H/2/outH);
      const p=(H/2)-y + bobAmt*0.4, posZ=0.5*H, rowDist=posZ/(p||1);
      const stepX=rowDist*(r1x-r0x)/outW, stepY=rowDist*(r1y-r0y)/outW;
      let fx=posX+rowDist*r0x, fy=posY+rowDist*r0y;
      for(let i=0;i<outW;i++){ let u=fx-Math.floor(fx); if(u<0)u+=1; let v=fy-Math.floor(fy); if(v<0)v+=1;
        let tx=(u*ctw)|0, ty=(v*cth)|0; const s=((ty*ctw+tx)<<2), d=((j*outW+i)<<2);
        out[d]=ceilTexData[s]; out[d+1]=ceilTexData[s+1]; out[d+2]=ceilTexData[s+2]; out[d+3]=255; fx+=stepX; fy+=stepY; }
    } cb.putImageData(img,0,0); ctx.imageSmoothingEnabled=false; ctx.drawImage(c,0,0,W,H/2);
  }
  // Chão com bob
  if(floorReady && floorTexData){
    const {ctx:fb,canvas:c,outW,outH}=ensureHalfBuffer('floor',2);
    const img=fb.createImageData(outW,outH), out=img.data;
    const r0x=dirX-planeX, r0y=dirY-planeY, r1x=dirX+planeX, r1y=dirY+planeY;
    for(let j=0;j<outH;j++){ const y=(H/2/outH)*j + 0.5*(H/2/outH);
      const posZ=0.5*H + bobAmt*0.4, rowDist=posZ/(y||1);
      const stepX=rowDist*(r1x-r0x)/outW, stepY=rowDist*(r1y-r0y)/outW;
      let fx=posX+rowDist*r0x, fy=posY+rowDist*r0y;
      for(let i=0;i<outW;i++){ let u=fx-Math.floor(fx); if(u<0)u+=1; let v=fy-Math.floor(fy); if(v<0)v+=1;
        let tx=(u*ftw)|0, ty=(v*fth)|0; const s=((ty*ftw+tx)<<2), d=((j*outW+i)<<2);
        out[d]=floorTexData[s]; out[d+1]=floorTexData[s+1]; out[d+2]=floorTexData[s+2]; out[d+3]=255; fx+=stepX; fy+=stepY; }
    } fb.putImageData(img,0,0); ctx.imageSmoothingEnabled=false; ctx.drawImage(c,0,H/2,W,H/2);
  }
  // Paredes + zBuffer
  if(wallReady){
    for(let x=0;x<W;x++){ const camX=2*x/W-1; const rdx=dirX+planeX*camX, rdy=dirY+planeY*camX;
      let mapX=posX|0, mapY=posY|0; const ddx=Math.abs(1/(rdx||1e-9)), ddy=Math.abs(1/(rdy||1e-9));
      let stepX=(rdx<0)?-1:1, stepY=(rdy<0)?-1:1;
      let sideX=(rdx<0? (posX-mapX)*ddx : (mapX+1.0-posX)*ddx);
      let sideY=(rdy<0? (posY-mapY)*ddy : (mapY+1.0-posY)*ddy);
      let side=0, dist=0, tile=0;
      while(true){ if(sideX<sideY){ sideX+=ddx; mapX+=stepX; side=0; } else { sideY+=ddy; mapY+=stepY; side=1; }
        if(mapX<0||mapY<0||mapX>=MAP_W||mapY>=MAP_H) break;
        tile=worldMap[mapY][mapX];
        if(tile===1 || (tile===2 && !doorOpen)){ dist=(side===0? sideX-ddx : sideY-ddy); break; }
      }
      zBuffer[x]=dist;
      const lh=Math.max(1,(H/(dist||1e-9))|0); const y0=-lh/2+H/2 + Math.sin(bobT)*2;
      let wallX = (side===0) ? posY + dist*rdy : posX + dist*rdx; wallX -= Math.floor(wallX);
      let texX = (wallX * wallImg.width) | 0;
      if(side===0 && rdx>0) texX = wallImg.width - texX - 1;
      if(side===1 && rdy<0) texX = wallImg.width - texX - 1;
      const texImg = (tile===2 ? (doorReady?doorImg:wallImg) : wallImg);
      ctx.drawImage(texImg, texX, 0, 1, texImg.height, x, y0, 1, lh);
      // Sombreamento mais forte (realista)
      const shade = 1 - Math.exp(-dist*0.15) + (side?0.08:0);
      if(shade>0){ ctx.fillStyle='rgba(0,0,0,'+Math.min(0.75,shade).toFixed(3)+')'; ctx.fillRect(x,y0,1,lh); }
    }
  }
  // Sprites (oclusão por zBuffer) + sombras no chão
  if(enemyReady){
    const list=enemies.map((s)=>({s, d:(s.x-posX)**2+(s.y-posY)**2})).sort((a,b)=>b.d-a.d);
    for(const it of list){ const s=it.s; if(!s.alive) continue;
      const dx=s.x-posX, dy=s.y-posY;
      const invDet=1/(planeX*dirY - dirX*planeY); const tx=invDet*(dirY*dx - dirX*dy); const ty=invDet*(-planeY*dx + planeX*dy);
      if(ty<=0) continue;
      const sx=(W/2)*(1+tx/ty); const size=Math.abs((H/ty))|0;
      const drawY = (H/2 - size/2) + Math.sin(bobT)*2;
      // sombra elíptica
      const alpha = clamp(0.6 - ty*0.06, 0.05, 0.35);
      ctx.save(); ctx.globalAlpha=alpha; ctx.fillStyle='#000'; ctx.beginPath(); ctx.ellipse(sx, H/2 + size*0.25, size*0.4, size*0.12, 0, 0, Math.PI*2); ctx.fill(); ctx.restore();
      // desenha por colunas com zBuffer
      const startX = Math.max(0, (sx-size/2)|0), endX = Math.min(W-1, (sx+size/2)|0);
      for(let x=startX;x<=endX;x++){ const stripe = (x - (sx-size/2)) / size; if(ty > 0 && ty < zBuffer[x]){
          const texX = (stripe * enemyImg.width) | 0;
          ctx.drawImage(enemyImg, texX, 0, 1, enemyImg.height, x, drawY, 1, size);
          if(s.hitFlash>0){ const a=(s.hitFlash*4).toFixed(3); ctx.fillStyle='rgba(255,60,60,'+a+')'; ctx.fillRect(x, drawY, 1, size); }
      } }
      // barra de vida
      const bw=Math.max(40, size*0.6); const bx=clamp(sx-bw/2, 0, W-bw), by=drawY-10;
